DATADIR="C://Users//Hasan//Desktop//DataSet"
CATEGORES=["Negative","Positive"]
Negative=["Negative"]
Positive=["Positive"]
In [6]:
#Veri setinde ka tane resim olduunu gsterir

training_data = []
def create_training_data():
    for category in CATEGORES:
        path = os.path.join(DATADIR,category)
        class_num = CATEGORES.index(category)
        for img in os.listdir(path):
            try:
                img_array = cv2.imread(os.path.join(path,img))
                training_data.append([img_array,class_num])
            except Exception as e:
                pass
create_training_data()
print(len(training_data))

In [11]:
#Positive snfn datasnn RGB kanallarn histogram zerinden gsteriyoruz

red_channel = img_array[:, :, 0]
# Plot the red histogram with bins in a range of 256
plt.hist(red_channel.ravel(), bins=256)
# Set title and show
plt.title('Red Histogram')
plt.show()
# Obtain the green channel
green_channel = img_array[:, :, 1]
plt.hist(green_channel.ravel(), bins=256)
plt.title('Green Histogram')
plt.show()
# Obtain the blue channel
blue_channel = img_array[:, :, 2]
plt.hist(blue_channel.ravel(), bins=256)
plt.title('Blue Histogram')
plt.show()
# Combined Histogram
plt.hist(red_channel.ravel(), bins = 256, color = 'red', alpha = 0.5)
plt.hist(green_channel.ravel(), bins = 256, color = 'green', alpha = 0.5)
plt.hist(blue_channel.ravel(), bins = 256, color = 'blue', alpha = 0.5)
plt.xlabel('Intensity Value')
plt.ylabel('Count')
plt.legend(['Red_Channel', 'Green_Channel', 'Blue_Channel'])
plt.title('Combined Histogram')
plt.show()

#Her bir resmin yksekliini ve geniliini veren dizi setidir.

img_height =[]
img_width = []
for category in CATEGORES:
    path = os.path.join(DATADIR , category)
    for img in os.listdir(path):
        img_array = cv2.imread(os.path.join(path,img))
        img_array = cv2.cvtColor(img_array, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)
        img_height.append(img_array.shape[0])
        img_width.append(img_array.shape[1])
